---
import "../styles/global.css";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";

const title = "Terms of Service - Xelleq";
const description = "Celliq's term & condition";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />

    <!-- Open Graph (for sharing on social media) -->
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <!-- Optional: <meta property="og:image" content="/social-preview.png" /> -->

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={title} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <h1 class="page-title mt-4">Xelleq Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="container mt-4 mb-4">
        <p>Last updated: 04 August 2025</p>

        <p>Welcome to <strong>Xelleq</strong>. By creating an account or using our services, you agree to the following terms. Please read them carefully.</p>

        <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>Xelleq is intended for users aged 13 and older. By registering, you confirm that you are at least 13 years old. We collect date of birth during registration to help enforce this policy.</p>

        <h2>2. Account Responsibility</h2>
        <p>Users must create an account using a username, password, and valid email address. Your username is public, but your email remains private. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and any activity under your account.</p>

        <h2>3. Content Usage</h2>
        <p>Users may upload and share content such as text, images, videos, documents, and audio across chatrooms, forums, and server file storage.</p>
        <ul>
        <li>Public servers allow only admins to upload files.</li>
        <li>Private servers allow anyone to upload files.</li>
        <li>All content must comply with our content policy (see Section 4).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Prohibited Content</h2>
        <p>Users must not upload or share content that is:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>Illegal or promotes illegal activity</li>
        <li>Harassing, threatening, or hateful</li>
        <li>Sexually explicit or violent</li>
        <li>Spam or misleading (e.g. phishing, scams)</li>
        <li>In violation of copyright or intellectual property</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Violations may result in content removal or account suspension without prior notice.</p>

        <h2>5. Voice and Media Features</h2>
        <p>Xelleq uses third-party service <strong>Agora</strong> for voice calls. By using the voice feature, you agree to their <a href="https://www.agora.io/en/terms-of-service/" target="_blank">terms of service</a> as well.</p>

        <h2>6. Privacy and Data</h2>
        <p>We collect and store the following user data:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>Username, email address, and date of birth</li>
        <li>Profile description and profile image (optional)</li>
        <li>Chat messages, forum activity, uploaded files</li>
        <li>Liked posts, saved posts, and your own posts</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Data is stored securely, but users are advised to avoid uploading sensitive personal information.</p>

        <h2>7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms as our platform evolves. You will be notified of significant changes. Continued use of Xelleq means you agree to the updated terms.</p>

        <h2>8. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Cambodia. If you access Xelleq from outside Cambodia, you do so at your own risk and are responsible for complying with local laws.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these terms, please contact us at: <strong>support@xelleq.com</strong>.</p>

        <p>Thank you for using Xelleq. Made with Love.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
